= Install

== Requires
Python3, GTK environment

== Meson

=== Debain repository
python-pip3

pip3 install meson

==== Ninja
Get ninja and install. Will need a modern 'ninja'. Use pre-builds for 
64bit, 32bit users will need to build their own (currently).



== Meson
cd ../SiteBuilder
mkdir build
/usr/local/bin/meson.py build
cd build
sudo ninja schema-install

